data.eml:eml: Synonymical notes on Neotropical Cerambycidae (Insecta, Coleoptera)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Monné, Miguel A., R, Juan Pablo Botero (2011): Synonymical notes on Neotropical Cerambycidae (Insecta, Coleoptera). Zootaxa 2928: 64-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.278005
